  "getThere": "Fly into Townsville Airport (TSV) or drive south to Ayr (~90 minutes). Most operators depart from Alva Beach near Ayr — a 30-minute boat ride straight east to the wreck. Longer day-boat and liveaboard runs also leave from Townsville and Magnetic Island (2–3 hours each way). Open ocean crossing, often choppy; chartered crossings are weather-dependent.",
